pyopengl: pyopengl (cross platform Python binding to OpenGL)
pyopengl:
pyopengl: PyOpenGL is the cross platform Python binding to OpenGL and related
pyopengl: APIs. It includes support for OpenGL v1.1, GLU, GLUT v3.7, GLE 3 and
pyopengl: WGL 4. It also includes support for dozens of extensions (where 
pyopengl: supported in the underlying implementation).
pyopengl: PyOpenGL is interoperable with a large number of external GUI
pyopengl: libraries for Python including (Tkinter, wxPython, FxPy, PyGame,
pyopengl: and Qt).
pyopengl: http://pyopengl.sourceforge.net/
pyopengl: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
